    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the synthesis evidence node consolidating seven prior studies was judged by reviewers to provide sufficient empirical grounding, and the Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate hemolysis index below the clinical threshold at the 95th percentile across all operating points. Several credibility factor gaps remain at MRL 5, but the decision was made to accept with documented limitations. Note: the synthesis evidence node was not formally marked as foundational evidence in the provenance graph, an encoding omission that was not caught during review.",
